Well well well this song has brought some special senses with it, 
Perfect timing and amazing relatable lyrics! Momina got those thrilling 
fluctuation and vibration in her voice, reminds me of Nazia Hassan!!
Asim; honestly I wasn't expecting much from him but this is (BOOM!!) 
very well sung! His eyebrow game is strong lol 😉 
Best lines : "karday koi, nawazishain karam, meherbaaniyan." By asim.
"Phir gir paray, koi mila na sahara.. kia karain?" Andddd.. "Kia ho 
gaya.. socha na tha" By Momina. 💖
BET YOU PAKISTAN'S COKE STUDIO IS THOUSAND TIMES BETTER THAN INDIA'S 
COKE STUDIO ON THE BASIS OF "LYRICS" and "SOUND EDITING". 
PAKISTAN ZINDABAAD. 👏
